    "title": "Scatterplots & Line of Best Fit (Easy)",
    "body": "A line of best fit, y = mx + b, models a scatterplot. The slope m is the predicted change in y for each 1-unit increase in x; b is the predicted y when x = 0. Plug in x to predict y.",
